channel.description:
[center][img]http://img541.imageshack.us/img541/8732/6zfw.png[/img]
Biohazard is a Runescape Private Server that thrives for perfection. Just wanted to mention that I'm already 5 years into rsps coding. There are so many features, details, bosses and areas that makes this Runescape Private Server unique from other servers. If you have interest in this server, and want to enjoy a friendly community, then this is the place to go! We hope you have a great stay!
[b] [img]http://abyss-rsps.com/advert/hometz.png[/img] - [url=http://www.biohazard-rsps.com/]Home[/url] [img]http://abyss-rsps.com/advert/forumts.png[/img] - [url=http://www.biohazard-rsps.com/forum.php]Forums[/url] [img]http://abyss-rsps.com/advert/playt.png[/img] - [url=http://www.biohazard-rsps.com/webclient/]Play Now[/url] [img]http://abyss-rsps.com/advert/highscoret.gif[/img] - [url=http://www.biohazard-rsps.com/highscores/highscores.php]Highscores[/url] [img]http://abyss-rsps.com/advert/votet.gif[/img] - [url=http://www.biohazard-rsps.com/vote/]Forums[/url][/b][/center][center][size=36pt]Features: [/size]
[b] -Many bosses -Many areas -Fishing Trawler -Decent skilling + many areas to explore -Sailing (100%) -Custom Random's -Runescape Random's -Sailing Crash -Dungeon Collapse -Desert hallucination -Ranging Guild -Warriors' Guild -Skillcape masters -Full Dagganoth Lair -Pest control rewards -Full godwars -Close to perfect combat -And so much more!!!
[/b]
